Odaily Planet Daily News: Natalia Ameline of the Ethereum Layer2 Metis Foundation sent a letter to all community members today through the official Metis X, analyzing the stagnation of Ethereum in this cycle, and detailing the ReGenesis plan launched by Metis in January this year, indicating that Metis will serve as a transformer to save the Ethereum ecosystem and even lead the entire blockchain ecosystem upgrade, embracing the full Web3+AI.
The letter said that the core reason for Ethereum's poor performance in this round is that the social experiment of Web3 has ended, but Ethereum has failed to adapt to the new market environment in time.
Metis launched the ReGenesis plan to bet on the AI ​​ecosystem, supporting the Andromeda network upgrade + the underlying framework of the new high-performance architecture. ReGenesis also plans to build a complete AI+Web3 flywheel:
1. Andromeda + new chain architecture: provide high-performance AI computing and trading environment;
2. LazAI: decentralized AI training data to ensure AI value alignment;
3. DAT: integrate AI assets into the Web3 economy to create a new AI economic model;
4. Verified Computing: measure and trade AI assets to create an AI asset market;
5. Increase user and developer participation: promote the self-growth cycle of AI+Web3.
